Dugdale is going to be a music browser and jukebox.
A browser-based music browsing and request system will feed into streams (icecast or similar).

Q: Why Dugdale?
A: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Louis_Dugdale

This is presently using the litestream binaries 'litestream' and 'source' (included in /bin), and it assumes
running litestream separately like so: 

  bin/litestream 8000 127.0.0.1 8888 10 stream
